					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">foobaz wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">How can you delegate tile drawing to the hardware? Isn't there too much state that can change per scanline to make that possible?</div>
<br />PocketNES sets up three of the GBA's four DMA channels for HDMA, pointing at the GBA's equivalents of PPUSCROLL, PPUCTRL, and PPUMASK (BG0XOFS/BG0YOFS, BG0CNT, and DISPCNT respectively). The fourth is used to stream decoded DPCM (but not $4011 PCM, unfortunately for Big Bird fans).</div>

